text: Wilfredo León Venero (born 31 July 1993) is a Cuban volleyball player with Polish citizenship (since July 14, 2015), a member of Cuba men's national volleyball team in 2007–2012 and Russian club Zenit Kazan, silver medalist of the World Championship 2010, NORCECA Champion (2009, 2011), Cuban Champion (2009, 2010, 2011), Russian Champion (2015, 2016). ==Other websites== * Highlights (movie) * FIVB profile Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Cuban volleyball players Category:Polish volleyball players Category:Sportsmen
